data.name: HCS Major Kansas City 2022
data.description: Welcome back Halo community! Join us at the HCS Major Kansas City 2022, where the stage is set for our next Halo Infinite event! Who will be crowned the champion?

tournaments.name: HCS Major Kansas City 2022 4v4
tournaments.description: Teams from around the world will be competing at the HCS Major Kansas City 2022 for their chance at the $250,000+ prize pool!
tournaments.shortDescription: Teams from around the world will be competing at the HCS Major Kansas City 2022 for their chance at the $250,000+ prize pool!

tournaments.name: HCS Major Kansas City 2022 FFA
tournaments.description: HCS Major Kansas City 2022 features a free Halo FFA tournament, which will be open for up to 504 players and spectators. Best of luck to those competing for their shot at the $5,000 prize pool!
